## Project Structure

```
ubuntu/            # Build scripts (not board-specific)
boards/            # Board configs only
scripts/           # Helpers
tests/             # Ubuntu official test suite
docs/              # PORTING, ARCHITECTURE, BUILD
.rules             # This file
AGENTS.md -> .rules
```
